pub enum LedgerError {

    #[error("Solana app not open on Ledger device")]
    NoAppResponse = ,

    #[error("Ledger sdk exception")]
    SdkException = ,

    #[error("Ledger invalid parameter")]
    SdkInvalidParameter = ,

    #[error("Ledger overflow")]
    SdkExceptionOverflow = ,

    #[error("Ledger security exception")]
    SdkExceptionSecurity = ,

    #[error("Ledger invalid CRC")]
    SdkInvalidCrc = ,

    #[error("Ledger invalid checksum")]
    SdkInvalidChecksum = ,

    #[error("Ledger invalid counter")]
    SdkInvalidCounter = ,

    #[error("Ledger operation not supported")]
    SdkNotSupported = ,

    #[error("Ledger invalid state")]
    SdkInvalidState = ,

    #[error("Ledger timeout")]
    SdkTimeout = ,

    #[error("Ledger PIC exception")]
    SdkExceptionPic = ,

    #[error("Ledger app exit exception")]
    SdkExceptionAppExit = ,

    #[error("Ledger IO overflow exception")]
    SdkExceptionIoOverflow = ,

    #[error("Ledger IO header exception")]
    SdkExceptionIoHeader = ,

    #[error("Ledger IO state exception")]
    SdkExceptionIoState = ,

    #[error("Ledger IO reset exception")]
    SdkExceptionIoReset = ,

    #[error("Ledger CX port exception")]
    SdkExceptionCxPort = ,

    #[error("Ledger system exception")]
    SdkExceptionSystem = ,

    #[error("Ledger out of space")]
    SdkNotEnoughSpace = ,

    #[error("Ledger invalid counter")]
    NoApduReceived = ,

    #[error("Ledger operation rejected by the user")]
    UserCancel = ,

    #[error("Ledger received invalid Solana message")]
    SolanaInvalidMessage = ,

    #[error("Solana summary finalization failed on Ledger device")]
    SolanaSummaryFinalizeFailed = ,

    #[error("Solana summary update failed on Ledger device")]
    SolanaSummaryUpdateFailed = ,

    #[error("Ledger received unimplemented instruction")]
    UnimplementedInstruction = ,

    #[error("Ledger received invalid CLA")]
    InvalidCla = ,
}

defs.name: RemoteWalletError
defs.value:
pub enum RemoteWalletError {

    #[error("hidapi error")]
    Hid(String),

    #[error("device type mismatch")]
    DeviceTypeMismatch,

    #[error("device with non-supported product ID or vendor ID was detected")]
    InvalidDevice,

    #[error("invalid derivation path: {0}")]
    InvalidDerivationPath(String),

    #[error("invalid input: {0}")]
    InvalidInput(String),

    #[error("invalid path: {0}")]
    InvalidPath(String),

    #[error(transparent)]
    LedgerError(
                #[from]
                LedgerError),

    #[error("no device found")]
    NoDeviceFound,

    #[error("protocol error: {0}")]
    Protocol(&'static str),

    #[error("pubkey not found for given address")]
    PubkeyNotFound,

    #[error("remote wallet operation rejected by the user")]
    UserCancel,
}
